---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for the CTAI website."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-ink-200 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-ink-300 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Non-Official Project</h2>
        <p>
          CTAI is a personal, non-official project. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or
          representative of any Baha&rsquo;i institution, the Universal House of Justice, or any other
          religious body. All AI-generated analysis, annotations, and alignments are offered as
          scholarly tools and should not be treated as authoritative.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Use of Content</h2>
        <p>
          The sacred texts presented on this site are the translations of Shoghi Effendi and are
          in the public domain. AI-generated annotations, alignments, and analysis are provided
          for educational and research purposes. Use them at your own discretion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">No Warranty</h2>
        <p>
          This site is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. AI-generated content may
          contain errors. We make no guarantees about the accuracy, completeness, or reliability
          of any analysis, alignment, or annotation on this site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-display text-ink-200 mb-2">Newsletter</h2>
        <p>
          By voluntarily signing up on this site, you agree to receive occasional email
          communications about new content, features, or updates. You may opt out of these
          communications at any time by using the unsubscribe link in any email or by
          contacting us directly.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
